{
  "texts": [
    "• In banking: Banks have intensively and successfully used chatbots to interact with customers for services such as bill settlement, account balance checks, banking card activation or cancellation, feedback collection, and new service suggestions [49].",
    "• In food and restoration industries: Several companies in the food and restaurant industry own customized chatbots that interact with their clients to provide the necessary information whenever required.",
    "Their chatbots assist them in acknowledging received orders, providing delivery information to customers, and helping them track their orders [49,50].",
    "Identified literature gaps• Insufficient integration of AI Chatbots in Industry 5.0 setups: The literature review above shows that GenAI applications like chatbots are popular in various sectors (education, healthcare, customer support, banking, and food restauration), producing outstanding results and improving user experiences [20].",
    "However, their use and integration within the operational manufacturing field are still scarce [16], especially when considering an Industry 5.0 human-centric context for small to medium-sized manufacturing enterprises."
  ]
}